# Ignore transient + secret artifacts; keep curated knowledge and canonical context.
*
!.gitignore
!knowledge/
!knowledge/**
!skills/
!skills/plan-debate/
!skills/plan-debate/**
!skills/cross-review/
!skills/cross-review/**
!skills/worktree-orchestrate/
!skills/worktree-orchestrate/**
!skills/merge-when-green/
!skills/merge-when-green/**
!*.md
!SETTINGS.json
backup/
dispatch/
workunits/
WORKFLOW_STATE.json
# AI-enrichment output: non-deterministic (LLM + repo profile, varies per run /
# engine / model). Listed AFTER !*.md so its AGENTS.md/CLAUDE.md are NOT
# re-included by that allowlist. A static reviewed snapshot lives in
# docs/examples/ai-context-sample/.
ai-context/
